Like the central government, various state governments have increased their spending on infrastructural projects as evident from capital expenditure towards infrastructure in their state budgets. The spending has increased by 4 times between FY 2013 and FY 2023 resulting in total spends of ~12 Tn (US$145 Bn) in FY 2023.
